{"tid":1516682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］沙田新城市個連儂牆又俾人搣曬！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:43:11.000Z","uid":157282,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3fdceaaed2d2371b4bad61a7f868c4bc5589f94a","tid":1516682,"uid":157282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"每日翻工行過新城市，明明牆上面都貼滿曬反送中嘅文宣，<br />\n但係夜晚收工嗰陣幅牆乾乾淨淨乜都冇。<br />\n直至我今日見到下面呢班人係到撕紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quSFd4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquSFd4e.png&h=be5ae139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就走埋去問佢做乜撕曬佢啦，個妹妹答我：<br />\n<br />\n每晚新城市啲清潔工都會清曬佢，啲街坊唔想曬咗啲文宣，就每晚自發落來拆文宣，然後第二日再起返幅牆。<br />\n<br />\n撕紙嗰班街坊當中仲有唔少人係銀髮族，其中一個婆婆仲要係咁呼籲身邊嘅人831遮打見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田柚好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b296b8ae6f76dde9382e113793b67a708283c133","tid":1516682,"uid":231818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"ae3d05a58226ec7a303de6982e03c50c374470d1","tid":1516682,"uid":35337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fdceaaed2d2371b4bad61a7f868c4bc5589f94a","tid":1516682,"uid":157282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"每日翻工行過新城市，明明牆上面都貼滿曬反送中嘅文宣，<br />\n但係夜晚收工嗰陣幅牆乾乾淨淨乜都冇。<br />\n直至我今日見到下面呢班人係到撕紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quSFd4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquSFd4e.png&h=be5ae139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就走埋去問佢做乜撕曬佢啦，個妹妹答我：<br />\n<br />\n每晚新城市啲清潔工都會清曬佢，啲街坊唔想曬咗啲文宣，就每晚自發落來拆文宣，然後第二日再起返幅牆。<br />\n<br />\n撕紙嗰班街坊當中仲有唔少人係銀髮族，其中一個婆婆仲要係咁呼籲身邊嘅人831遮打見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田柚好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"咁做真係好環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d22dbf707b07faa5db6a0a5410643e1cea86cc","tid":1516682,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59a90e200b4775dc6994c4b739987f12f26ceb6","tid":1516682,"uid":137725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"啱晒啦<br />\n過期啲資訊梗係要搣<br />\n我哋癡返啲update嘅資訊仲好<br />\n唔該晒！"},{"pid":"3afbfe5319ae0f11d8ccae9e2db2d83d2103f80d","tid":1516682,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"沙田柚 香港第一"},{"pid":"86ecf332d88b75912082a2ebbd4e080ee52c8597","tid":1516682,"uid":285117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"沙田柚真係勁抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf2c95416669603fa484af14ad61efd6d12dce3","tid":1516682,"uid":265171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"比你嚇死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次唔好做標題黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd9a1cb69722b9eb4cdef2cb56c975b5f366bd1","tid":1516682,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"沙田友真係高質, 連小妹妹都咁識諗"},{"pid":"ad97ddef5f5517c24d759c0bec3c31b603703476","tid":1516682,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"唔錯wor沙田友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f9e25392b5efa1e2c73268dfa18c479421f260","tid":1516682,"uid":157282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcf2c95416669603fa484af14ad61efd6d12dce3","tid":1516682,"uid":265171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"比你嚇死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次唔好做標題黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"好的，我會改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f95458d623032213cf8d237c9d37b0f7717623d","tid":1516682,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36372f9cf7d624208fcd73282dd8d37eac0dcb38","tid":1516682,"uid":40567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔係好耐喇咩"}]}